<S ID='S-56' IA='BKG' AZ='OTH'> The structure is almost the same as <REFAUTHOR>Gunji</REFAUTHOR> 's structure except for explicitly showing complex proposition , subordinate-clause and conjunctive-particle that are newly added to deal with complex sentences . </S>
