<S ID='S-176' IA='OWN' AZ='OWN'> In sum , with these constraints , a constraint satisfaction process in UG based parsing can be done locally and consequently very efficiently . </S>
<S ID='S-177' IA='OTH' AZ='OWN'> In other words , primarily a constraint satisfaction process of a subordinate clause can be done within the analysis of subordinate clause , and that of the main clause can be done within it except for using motivated whose value has already been constrained in the subordinate clause . </S>
